    'A clinician-rated scale for assessment of primary degenerative dementia, staging cognitive decline from normal aging through severe dementia across 7 stages.', 'dementia', '1.0',
    'Current cognitive and functional status', 'Based on clinical interview and observation, select the stage that best characterizes the patient''s current level of cognitive and functional decline.',
