aluation. Discuss findings with patient and explore their experiences", "above_threshold_moderate": "Recommend comprehensive ASD evaluation. Consider referral to specialist (psychologist, psychiatrist, or neurologist with ASD expertise)", "above_threshold_high": "Strongly recommend comprehensive ASD evaluation by specialist. High likelihood of ASD diagnosis; prioritize referral"}, "limitations": ["Self-report measure may be affected by insight and self-awareness", "Not validated for individuals with intellectual disability", "Cannot differentiate ASD from other conditions with overlapping features", "Lower specificity means many false positives; positive screen requires follow-up"], "references": ["Eriksson JM, Andersen LM, Bejerot S. RAADS-14 Screen: validity of a screening tool for autism spectrum disorder in an adult psychiatric population. Mol Autism. 2013;4(1):49.", "Ritvo RA, Ritvo ER, Guthrie D, et al. The Ritvo Autism Asperger Diagnostic Scale-Revised (RAADS-R). J Autism Dev Disord. 2011;41(8):1076-1089."]}'::jsonb)
